high_descs: Walk to the right side of the toilet and face the tub.
Pick up the bottle of lotion in front of the second candle.
Walk in front of the toilet and face the tub.
Put the bottle of lotion down on the counter to the right of the tub.
Turn to the right to face the toilet.
Pick up the remaining bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet.
Turn to face the tub.
Put the bottle of lotion to the right of the first bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion to be near the tub.

high_descs: walk around the toilet and stand facing the left side.
Pick up the closest lotion bottle on the back of the toilet.
walk to the bath tub.
Set the lotion bottle on the back of the tub.
Approach the front of the toilet.
Pick up the second bottle of lotion from the toilet.
Turn around while holding the lotion.
Set the lotion bottle on the back of the tub next to the first bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move the lotion bottles from the toilet to the tub.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, turn left, move forward, then turn left to face the toilet.
Take the soap nearest to you from the back of the toilet.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right to face the counter, to the right of the tub.
Put the soap on the counter, to the left of the candle.
Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the soap from the back of the toilet.
Turn right, move forward, then turn around to face the counter to the right of the tub.
Put the soap on the counter, to the right of the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps on the counter.

high_descs: Head to the toilet
Grab the bottle of soap that is on top of the toilet
Move slightly to the left
Put the bottle down on the right side of the tub
Move forward and face the toilet on your right
Grab the bottle of soap that is on top of the toilet
Turn to your right and face the tub
Put the bottle down on the right side of the tub
anns.task_desc: Putting two bottles of soap on a counter near the tub

high_descs: Move to the right side of the toilet to the left of the shower.
Pick up a dispenser from the back of the toilet.
Move slightly over to the left  facing the tub.
Place the dispenser on the counter to the right of the tub.
Move to the front of the toilet in front of you.
Pick up a dispenser from the back of the toilet.
Move to the right side of the toilet in front of you.
Place the dispenser on the counter to the right of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move the two dispensers from the toilet to the counter on the right of the tub.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to face the right side of the toilet
Pick up the nearest lotion bottle from the top of the toilet
Move slightly left then turn back right to face the bathtub
Put the lotion bottle down on the surface just right of the bathtub
Walk around to the front side of the toilet and turn to face it
Pick up the lotion bottle from the top of the toilet
Turn left and face toward the bathtub
Put the lotion bottle down on the surface just right of the other bottle
anns.task_desc: Put the lotion bottles on the surface next to the bathtub
